title: Wer traut sich da mich zu towerdiven?!

embed.description: I made a cool play and needed to share this with somebody. Im right now a Nami Main with about 500 games in ranked on her but wanted to practice some normals with Soraka and Leona. Hope you also feel so sick like me while I did this. https://www.leagueofgraphs.com/summoner/euw/JuicyJuju https://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=juicyjuju

body: War ein Normal und wirklich nix besonderes, aber die Stelle fand ich trotzdem sehr cool.
